##Wumart "expired for 8 years" follow-up: part of the claim is still on the way

Micro Signal ZhongJing-Show

Function introduction, grow in step with Chinese enterprises, talk with business leaders, spread business ideals, serve business people, "China Business News" control of the absolute voice of Chinese business.

The following article is from China Business News, written by Xu Liqing and Li Xianglei

Grow in step with Chinese enterprises, talk to business leaders, spread business ideals, serve business people, and China business daily controls the absolute voice of Chinese business.

Our reporter, Xu Liqing, Li Xianglei, reporting from Beijing

It has been seven days since the "problem mask" incident came to light on February 20. Beijing Wumart Commercial Group Co. , Ltd. (Wumart) did not make a public statement or apology on the matter. As of February 26, many consumers who purchased the SAS N958617 Mask, the Maksks  Mask and the Prestige Ameritech Face Masks at Wumart dot had not received corresponding compensation.

A few days ago, a number of consumers in Wumart rushed to buy masks said he received masks there are expired, no production date and other issues. According to the investigation of the reporter of China Business News, since 23, some consumers have received "refund one to three" compensation.

However, as of 5 p.m. on Feb. 26, more than half of the consumers in the rights group had not received compensation from Wumart stores, according to data obtained by China business news reporters from the rights group, a voluntary group of consumers. Among them, some consumers are in the store or customer service communication stage, there are also consumers reported that no Wumart stores contact themselves. According to incomplete statistics, the three kinds of masks have been recovered more than 1300, but there are still more than 2800, the total price of nearly 25000 yuan masks have not been recovered.

But outside the rights group, it is unclear whether any consumers have not been compensated, and Wumart has not released official figures.

Wang Dongyue of Zhongyou law firm said it was a fraud to sell expired masks without a production date, and that Wumart should refund 1 to 3 under Article fifty-five of the Consumer Protection Law. "At present, there are a large number of substandard masks in use. It is a great safety hazard for consumers to wear substandard masks in public places. Wumart should come out and publicly explain and recall them. "

A reporter from China Business News sent an interview letter to Wumart on the overall size of the mask, the recall, the compensation package and whether it would issue a public apology at the request of consumers. However, as of press time, no reply had been received.

Multi-channel claim

As of the press release of the China Business News, according to incomplete statistics on the group of rights defenders organized spontaneously by consumers, only within the group of 100 rights defenders, wumei Muxiyuan store, Yulin Li store, Sun Island store, Wanshou road store, Yuquan Road store, anwai store, Desheng store, Zengguang road store, Panjiayuan store, yuting bridge store, Guangming Building Store, dujiakan store, Tiantongyuan store, 13 stores have already compensated some consumers who bought Wumei Sas n958617 Mask Mask according to a refund of one to three; The West Gate, Anwai, Desheng, Huixin and Yushiqiao stores have offered a refund of one to three for consumers who purchased Maksks  masks Taihe Garden store, anwai store, Desheng store, Huixin store, yuting bridge store, Songzhuang store, Ganluyuan store on the sale of Prestige Ameritech Face Masks also carried out a refund of 3-1 compensation. According to incomplete statistics, more than 1,300 of the above-mentioned 3 types of face masks have been recovered so far. Regarding the stores and relevant data involved, the reporter from China business daily checked with Wumart. As of press time, no reply had been received from Wumart.

Zhang Qiang (not her real name) , who bought the mask at Wumart, told the China business daily about her claim that she first called multipoint customer service on Feb. 20 and received the compensation on Feb. 23, which lasted three days. As of press time, reporters from China Business News found incomplete statistics on the rights advocacy group organized by consumers themselves, that is, from the 23rd, one after another, consumers who have purchased Wumart masks have succeeded in obtaining a one-to-three refund from Wumart.

Although compensation has been awarded, the experience of many consumers seeking compensation has not been easy. Zhang Qiang told the China business news reporter, she can get compensation in 3 days has been considered more efficient. "Over the past few days, we have continued to make calls to 12345 and 12315, and some consumers have contacted the food and Drug Administration to seek a solution. But there are still a lot of consumers who are talking to stores."

Zhang Qiang these days is the experience of most of the consumer claims to Wumart a microcosm. According to a number of consumers who buy Wumart masks, they are basically through the above approach to contact the store.

Another consumer who has already received Wumart compensation told China business daily that when he went to Wumart related stores to make a claim, he would first sign an agreement, and after signing it, he would be compensated accordingly. Wang Dongyue, a lawyer with Zhongyou law firm, said: "The main reason for signing this settlement agreement with consumers is to avoid new civil disputes in the future. "

The claim is still on the way

Like most consumers who buy Wumart masks, it is her daily routine to call 12315,12345, multipoint customer service and Wumart counter. Fortunately, Zhang Qiang finally got the corresponding wumart compensation.

However, as of press time, there are still many consumers have not yet received Wumart response, the incident has not been resolved accordingly. China Business News reporter found that in a group of more than 100 people Wumart mask rights, there are still some consumers have not been compensated.

As of the press release of the China Business News, according to incomplete statistics on the group of rights defenders organized spontaneously by consumers, among the group of 100 rights defenders, about 17 boxes of 850 Maksks  masks were sold in 15 Wumart stores including Shuangyu Huandao, Panjiayuan, Qinghe, Huixin, Beiwa Road Erdian and Zhixin. Only three consumers said they had successfully won compensation. Wu Dian Road Store, Fan Yang Road store, Wang Jing Qilin she store, Tian Tong Yuan store, Yungang hypermarket store, Chaoyang Road store, Beitaipingzhuang store, Shahe Store 8 stores have not sold 9 boxes, a total of 180 SAS N958617 Mask Mask Repair; Prestige Ameritech Face Masks have been sold in 23 stores, and 36 boxes of 1,800 Masks have yet to be refunded at 3-1. As a result, a total of 2,830 masks have not been recovered or properly disposed of. Reporters on the above-mentioned data to the Wumart side for verification, as of press release, not received the official data of Wumart.

However, according to the statements of many consumers who bought Wumart masks, at present, apart from individual stores, some consumers who have not yet received compensation have already contacted Wumart stores or relevant staff. The other party said that the specific compensation is in the report, consumers are advised to wait until further notice. But a number of consumers said they had not yet contacted the stores. "I wanted to negotiate before going to the store, but Wumart hasn't contacted me, so I'm going straight to the store. "

Li Lei (not his real name) , who is actively communicating with Wumart about compensation, told China business daily: "I understand that some consumers who buy the same masks in Tiantongyuan as I have already received compensation, so I contacted the owner of Tiantongyuan twice to seek redress, but both times the owner denied it, and he has not given me a concrete solution so far. "

In view of the above-mentioned situation, "China business daily" reporter called the China Consumer Association, relevant staff said that the current State Administration of market supervision and regulation in the face masks, proposed to its reflection. Subsequently, relevant officials of the State Administration of market supervision and administration told the China business daily reporter that according to the emergency notice of the eight departments including the State Administration of Market Supervision and administration on launching special actions to crack down on the illegal manufacture and sale of masks and other protective products, the market supervision department and the Drug Supervision Department together with the relevant departments will focus on cracking down on the production and sale of three-nil products, such as those without production dates, manufacturers'names and addresses, and certificates of product quality, as well as the use of quality marks such as authentication marks, acts of trademark infringement, patent counterfeiting, counterfeiting, confusion, false publicity and false advertising.

Li Lei is not the only consumer facing claims in a community of self organized activists. As of press time, Wumart on the "issue mask" incident did not make a public statement or apology. Wumart on the "mask incident" specific compensation follow-up, "China Business News" reporters will continue to pay attention and follow-up reports.
